{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d226d111-1a70-472a-aeab-39fb02769bec","content":"Here's the plan and architecture:\n\n---\n\n## RAG Q&A — Architecture Plan\n\n### Current State\nBare .NET 10 Web API (`net10.0`, minimal API + controllers), two small markdown docs in `Docs/`.\n\n---\n\n### Proposed Architecture\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐  POST /ingest   ┌──────────────────┐\n│  Docs/*.md  │ ──────────────► │ Ingestion Service │\n└─────────────┘                 │  1. Read files    │\n                                │  2. Chunk text    │\n                                │  3. Embed chunks  │\n                                │  4. Store vectors │\n                                └────────┬─────────┘\n                                         ▼\n                                ┌──────────────────┐\n                                │  Vector Store     │\n                                │ (in-memory or     │\n                                │  Qdrant/pgvector) │\n                                └────────▲─────────┘\n                                         │\n┌─────────────┐  POST /ask      ┌────────┴─────────┐\n│   User      │ ──────────────► │  Query Service    │\n│  question   │ ◄────────────── │  1. Embed query   │\n│             │   grounded      │  2. Similarity    │\n└─────────────┘   answer        │     search        │\n                                │  3. Build prompt  │\n                                │     w/ chunks     │\n                                │  4. Call LLM      │\n                                └──────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Key Components\n\n| Component | Responsibility |\n|---|---|\n| **`Services/DocumentIngestionService`** | Reads `Docs/*.md`, splits into chunks (by heading / fixed-size with overlap), calls embedding API, stores vectors |\n| **`Services/VectorStoreService`** | Abstracts vector storage — start with an in-memory `IVectorStore`, swap to Qdrant/pgvector later |\n| **`Services/QueryService`** | Embeds the user question, performs cosine-similarity search (top-k), builds a grounded prompt, calls the LLM |\n| **`Controllers/IngestionController`** | `POST /api/ingest` — triggers doc ingestion |\n| **`Controllers/AskController`** | `POST /api/ask` — accepts `{ question }`, returns `{ answer, sources[] }` |\n| **`Models/`** | `DocumentChunk`, `AskRequest`, `AskResponse`, `IngestResponse` |\n\n### Chunking Strategy\n- **Primary split**: by markdown heading (`# / ## / ###`)\n- **Secondary split**: if a section exceeds ~500 tokens, split into fixed-size windows with ~100-token overlap\n- Each chunk retains metadata: `source file`, `heading path`, `chunk index`\n\n### NuGet Packages Needed\n- **`Microsoft.Extensions.AI`** — unified `IChatClient` / `IEmbeddingGenerator` abstractions (ships with .NET 10)\n- **`Microsoft.Extensions.VectorData`** — in-memory vector store abstraction\n- An AI provider package (e.g., `Azure.AI.OpenAI` or `Microsoft.Extensions.AI.OpenAI`)\n\n### Configuration (`appsettings.json`)\n- `AI:EmbeddingModel` / `AI:ChatModel` — model names\n- `AI:Endpoint` / `AI:ApiKey` — provider connection\n- `Rag:DocsPath` — path to markdown folder (default `Docs/`)\n- `Rag:ChunkSize` / `Rag:ChunkOverlap` — tuning knobs\n\n### Todos\n1. Add NuGet package references\n2. Create `Models/` DTOs\n3. Implement `VectorStoreService` (in-memory)\n4. Implement `DocumentIngestionService` (read → chunk → embed → store)\n5. Implement `QueryService` (embed query → search → LLM call)\n6. Add `IngestionController` and `AskController`\n7. Wire DI in `Program.cs`\n8. Add config section to `appsettings.json`\n\n---\n\nWant me to implement this?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7498d193-7c95-4233-aa83-36dc498c4a39","outputTokens":1036,"requestId":"3842:220345:6F4206B:78440EA:6A03E189"},"id":"f89e907a-bf4c-4e87-b26d-eb41dda8c259","timestamp":"2026-05-13T02:27:43.003Z","parentId":"5238e9d9-7604-4c4f-b073-6b383712646c"}
